{"id":300440,"date":[{"year":1954,"month":2,"day":21}],"page":"8","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"文化广场","column":"","genre":"","count":"564","ytitle":"","mtitle":"来吧!我们的亲人","ftitle":"","authors":["王峰"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"海军战士　王峰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从报纸上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从北京城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像疾风掠过海面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给我们带来了一个音讯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这，不管在俱乐部；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在饭桌旁；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在炮位上；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甚至，在梦中；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少张口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都念颂着一句心底的话:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啥时候才到来呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的亲人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的代表们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当你们还在整理行装的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京车站，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已飞去了我的心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看见:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席送别你们的情景，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘱咐得多么亲切呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手握得又是那么紧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是右手呀!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看的是多么的真。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我又看见了你们的队伍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车站上欢送你们的人群，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我却急待着绿旗的摆动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开车吧!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"司机同志!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难道，你不了解，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在远离祖国大陆的海岛上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还等待有，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千百万战士的心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从那天起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就在这海岛上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不管是北风呼呼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不管是大雪纷纷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山顶上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总是挤满着人群。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是亲人来了吧!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从那边飘来的黑点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吸住了我们的心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过来的又是一只渔船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪里是你们呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的亲人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把我们捉的那条大鱼留下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把床铺让给亲人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把山腰的道路扫净，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把我们的棉衣刷新，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也要把大炮擦亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更好的保卫着海防。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要把，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"练兵，学文化的新成绩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"告诉给自己的亲人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来了，你们真的来了!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看，你们脸上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还留有北方冰雪侵袭的印记，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冻坏了吧!同志!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"累得够受了吧!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的亲人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走!快打水让亲人们洗脚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快些!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点个火给亲人们取暖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我抓住了老李手中的水桶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我去!我去!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全屋的人都被吵醒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干什么呀!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你在说什么梦话。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快睡吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好迎接毛主席派来的亲人。"}]}